{"tid":2407321,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"38歲陳法拉情人節報喜 宣佈B女出世","createTime":"2021-02-14T03:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T01:21:21.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"99aa2993815a7e7d6fe88f84877118c211cdf143","tid":2407321,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T03:00:06.000Z","msg":"今日情人節，38歲人妻陳法拉在社交網報喜，宣佈囡囡「小米妮」出世，法拉於2019年嫁外籍老公Emmanuel Straschnov，之前一直沒宣佈懷孕喜訊，想不到今日趁情人節公告已為人母，並貼出三手互牽相片，溫馨滿瀉。<br />\n<br />\n法拉用中英文留言：「The past 10 months have been a wondrous journey, filled with unknowns, amazement, love, and lots of joy. Our hearts are full as new parents, and we look forward to every day with this little lady. 十月懷胎真是不容易，但由看到她的那一刻開始，就覺得甚麼都是值得的。我們滿心歡喜地開始做新手爸爸媽媽喇！」法拉並留言指是鼠年尾巴的寶寶，相信她的女兒是在農曆年前出世，現在才報喜。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210214/EXOEWAXYWBDK3JMIRHFIEBBAAU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210214%2FEXOEWAXYWBDK3JMIRHFIEBBAAU%2F&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLuQRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=8dcc66b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210214%2FEXOEWAXYWBDK3JMIRHFIEBBAAU%2F&h=1e661f69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210214/EXOEWAXYWBDK3JMIRHFIEBBAAU/</a>"},{"pid":"2ea86f083d8a6c746e17947bec6dd7355cab79d6","tid":2407321,"uid":75196,"like":30,"dislike":3,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T03:01:24.000Z","msg":"唔想講就一直都唔好講，懶神祕，而家又要講"},{"pid":"8baf42ce29b16819b32f0f583245f6279630ff67","tid":2407321,"uid":252659,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"99aa2993815a7e7d6fe88f84877118c211cdf143","tid":2407321,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T03:00:06.000Z","msg":"今日情人節，38歲人妻陳法拉在社交網報喜，宣佈囡囡「小米妮」出世，法拉於2019年嫁外籍老公Emmanuel Straschnov，之前一直沒宣佈懷孕喜訊，想不到今日趁情人節公告已為人母，並貼出三手互牽相片，溫馨滿瀉。<br />\n<br />\n法拉用中英文留言：「The past 10 months have been a wondrous journey, f